{"about_the_game":"\u300aAbyssalRestaurant\u300bis a cooking simulation as well as a restaurant management game using a physics engine.<br>Players will take on the role of a small restaurant operator and chef in a fantasy world, and experience the process of making a wide variety of food for customers.<br>The game consists of three main modules: receiving customers, making food, and shopping in the market.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/9231d927d98325d6b69c289e71112958.png?t=1725621676\" /></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Nearly 200 different ingredients.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />A dozen types of tastes and scents that change with temperature.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Customers not only comment on their own food but may also evaluate based on the aromas of food from neighboring tables.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Food can be cut and processed into any shape, even removing bones from meat cuts.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Customers of different races and ages each have their own tastes and communication styles.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Freely design each dish.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Independently customize every item on the restaurant's menu.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Customers will decide what to eat through intelligent conversations with the owner.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/f4facc92ef58d36ec45862cd5271caa4.png?t=1725621676\" />Players can share their culinary creations with their Steam friends.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/ACD008A006D83C13E315C1E0C68C6751.png?t=1725621676\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/9FF6B0526C5795310DE9A1CCF5EEE37A.gif?t=1725621676\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/ACD008A006D83C13E315C1E0C68C6751.png?t=1725621676\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/572F5916E2FE0EEC82E301B2D1ABE5A2.gif?t=1725621676\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/ACD008A006D83C13E315C1E0C68C6751.png?t=1725621676\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/extras/\u8054\u673a\u529f\u80fdE.gif?t=1725621676\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725621676","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021020/page.bg.jpg?t=17256216